  "prompt": "What is the size of global escorted tour industry?",
  "response": "As of my last update, the global escorted tour industry was experiencing growth due to increased demand for structured and hassle-free travel experiences. However, specific figures for the size of the industry can vary widely depending on the source and the metrics used (such as revenue or number of travelers).\n\nFor the most precise and up-to-date information, it would be best to refer to market research reports from reputable firms such as IBISWorld, Statista, or Euromonitor International. These reports often provide detailed analyses and projections of the industry size, key players, and trends. Keep in mind that the figures might have changed post-2023 due to various factors affecting the travel industry, including economic shifts, geopolitical events, and recovering global travel patterns post-pandemic.",
